## skill.toml Spec

```toml
[skill]
name = "weather_enhanced"       # snake_case, matches directory name
version = "1.0.0"               # semver
description = "Current and forecast weather for any location"
enabled = true                  # false = skip at startup

[skill.permissions]
network = true                  # can make HTTP calls
filesystem = false              # cannot read/write files (unless needed)
```

`name` must exactly match the directory name. Sentinel uses this to hot-reload.

