## Debugging a Skill

```bash
# Check if skill loaded
curl http://localhost:8000/api/skills | jq

# Check registry state
curl http://localhost:8000/api/skills/<name> | jq

# Run a skill directly (dev helper)
cd backend && python -c "
import asyncio
from skills.weather_enhanced.main import WeatherSkill
async def test():
    skill = WeatherSkill()
    await skill.on_load()
    result = await skill.execute('get_current_weather', {'location': 'Atlanta, GA'})
    print(result.model_dump_json(indent=2))
asyncio.run(test())
"
```
